Global Surge Protection Components Market Insights
Surge Protection Components Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 4.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Surge Protection Components Market Overview
The surge protection components market is projected to experience significant growth in the coming years. In India, the market was valued at approximately USD 123.4 million in 2024 and is expected to reach USD 178.9 million by 2030, reflecting a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.4% during this period. This growth is driven by increasing awareness of equipment protection across industrial and residential sectors, as well as rising investments in smart grid and renewable energy projects. Globally, the surge protection devices market was valued at USD 2.89 billion in 2022 and is anticipated to grow at a CAGR of 6.8% from 2023 to 2030, indicating a robust demand for surge protection solutions worldwide.

